OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FITV News reporter Mahatir Pasha speaks
OL,7,Fto faith schools facing closure over
OL,8,FVAT charges
OL,10,F"We are not Eton!" Mohammed Farid
OL,11,FChowdhury proclaims as he shows us
OL,12,Faround his Islamic faith school in
OL,13,Feast London.
OL,15,F"The Government will have everyone
OL,16,Fbelieve it's targeting the rich to
OL,17,Fbetter the poor, but the families
OL,18,Fwhich depend on our school are not
OL,19,Frich!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
