OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FChowdhury is the Chair of the board of
OL,7,FGovernors at Darul Hadis Latifiah. His
OL,8,Fschool, like all private schools has
OL,9,Fbeen hit with VAT from the new year, a
OL,10,Fmove he believes is unfair.
OL,12,F"I just cannot understand why they
OL,13,Fwould treat schools like ours as if
OL,14,Fwe're elite - we have so much to lose.
OL,15,FOur parents are largely working class,
OL,16,Fscrimping and saving by whatever means
OL,17,Fnecessary to send their boys here."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
