OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FCo-Headteacher Maruf Ahmed - who
OL,7,Fhimself was a student here - points
OL,8,Fout that Darul Hadis is funded
OL,9,Fentirely by fees and community
OL,10,Fdonations and is rated Outstanding by
OL,11,Fthe schools regulator, Ofsted, on a
OL,12,Fnumber of metrics. He told ITV News,
OL,13,F"Our school has been a pillar for the
OL,14,Fcommunity for many decades," and the
OL,15,Fimposition of VAT risks "crippling" it.
OL,17,FMaruf Ahmed, Co-Headteacher at Darul
OL,18,FHadis Latifiahm, says the faith school
OL,19,Findustry could be crippled by the new
OL,20,FVAT policy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
