OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FThe school says it has no choice but
OL,7,Fto pass the extra cost directly onto
OL,8,Fparents.
OL,10,F17-year-old Safwaan Jahan is one of
OL,11,Fthe institution's star pupils. His
OL,12,Facademic excellence recently won him
OL,13,Fan award. He still has three years of
OL,14,Fstudy left here, but this is now at
OL,15,Frisk.
OL,17,FBack home - Safwaan's widowed mother
OL,18,Fwho left work to raise him - is
OL,19,Fagonising about where she'll find the
OL,20,Fextra money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
