OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,F"The school plays a vital role in his
OL,7,Flife. I can't make cuts on my bills or
OL,8,Fmy mortgage, but I may have to make
OL,9,Fcuts on my son's education," Rehanaz
OL,10,FNoor tells me, which would be
OL,11,F"devastating for his life."
OL,13,FRehanaz Noor fears her son Safwaan's
OL,14,Feducation is at risk.
OL,16,FThe Government's decision on VAT will
OL,17,Fcause more pain on some schools and
OL,18,Ffamilies than others.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
