OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FThe Independent Schools Council (ISC)
OL,7,Fsays there are some 1000 private
OL,8,Fschools around England with a
OL,9,F'religious ethos or character' -
OL,10,Feducating over 370,000 pupils.
OL,12,FThe Association of Muslim Schools
OL,13,F(AMS) is warning the change in tax
OL,14,Fpolicy could make up to 75% of private
OL,15,FIslamic faith schools "financially
OL,16,Funviable".
