OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FA group of organisations representing
OL,7,Ffaith schools, including Christian,
OL,8,FJewish and Muslim industry bodies has
OL,9,Fappealed to the Government for a tax
OL,10,Fexemption.
OL,12,FThey estimate an exemption for low-fee
OL,13,Fprivate faith schools will only cost
OL,14,Fthe Treasury #32 million - just 2.1%
OL,15,Fof the #1.5 billion that VAT on
OL,16,Fschools in approximated to raise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
