OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FUnfortunately for this group, the
OL,7,FGovernment appears to show no sign of
OL,8,Fbacktracking on its VAT policy on
OL,9,Fprivate schools.
OL,11,FWhen we put these findings to the
OL,12,FEducation Secretary Bridget
OL,13,FPhillipson, she dismissed them as
OL,14,F"scaremongering" and "bogus data" from
OL,15,F"private school lobby groups".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
