OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,F"We've had a lot of scaremongering and
OL,7,Fbogus data from private school lobby
OL,8,Fgroups over a number of years. We
OL,9,Fannounced this policy some years ago,
OL,10,Fahead of the election, we'd always
OL,11,Fbeen clear it was our intention to
OL,12,Fmake this change," she said.
OL,14,FAdding, "I'm afraid there won't be any
OL,15,Fexemptions in this area because we
OL,16,Fhave to raise money to invest in the
OL,17,Fstate sector."
OL,19,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,20,Fsay exemptions won't be made for faith
OL,21,Fschools.
