OL,3,C'We are not Eton': The private faith
OL,4,Cschools facing closure over VAT changes
OL,6,FFor Bnos Beis Yakov, a strictly Jewish
OL,7,FSchool in north-west London though,
OL,8,Fthe impact of VAT is very real.
OL,10,FIts Chairman fears the school - which
OL,11,Feducates 125 girls - will collapse by
OL,12,FMarch this year if there's no change
OL,13,Fto the tax roll-out.
OL,15,FZvi Sobel told ITV News, "This one is
OL,16,Fa deal breaker, I cannot see a way
OL,17,Fround it."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
