OL,6,FHe stressed the importance of faith
OL,7,Fbased education for the Charedi Jewish
OL,8,Fcommunity and fears for what will
OL,9,Fhappen to his pupils in the event of
OL,10,Fhis school closing.
OL,12,F"It's heartbreaking, it breaks my
OL,13,Fheart, I cannot tell you how hard
OL,14,Fwe've worked to get where we are,"
OL,15,FSobel said.
OL,17,FZvi Sobel, Chairman of Bnos Beis
OL,18,FYakov, says the VAT rollout is a "deal
OL,19,Fbreaker" for the school.
